  "text": "This is a third in a series of studies aimed at profiling CNG structures at crystallographic resolution to facilitate drug design and provide 3D templates for rationalizing biochemical and cytological observations. The need for detailed RNA structures is clearly signalled in the literature on rational design of CNG-binding ligands [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
